OL,3,CJersey's Education Minister says he
OL,4,Ccannot support introducing bilingual
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FOne headteacher said: "This should be
OL,8,Fa non-starter. There are many greater,
OL,9,Fmore pressing needs to be addressed in
OL,10,Fschools."
OL,12,FEchoing this, another headteacher
OL,13,Fstated: "A ridiculous idea. Get the
OL,14,Fcurrent portfolio of school buildings
OL,15,Fup to scratch as they are woefully
OL,16,Finadequate. Ensure the current schools
OL,17,Fare staffed sufficiently with a talent
OL,18,Fpool to draw up, get this done first."
