OL,3,CJersey's Education Minister says he
OL,4,Ccannot support introducing bilingual
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FHe further notes the financial and
OL,8,Fstaffing implications, Deputy Ward
OL,9,Fcomments: "The amendment lists total
OL,10,Ffinancial implications in the region
OL,11,Fof #60,000 for a 12-month project
OL,12,Fmanager role. The likely minimum gross
OL,13,Fcost to the government for a project
OL,14,Fmanagement role is #72,000 per annum".
OL,16,FDeputy Sir Philip Bailhache argues the
OL,17,Fchanges would bring economic,
OL,18,Fpolitical and diplomatic advantages,
OL,19,Fas well as cultural and heritage
OL,20,Fbenefits, given the island's
OL,21,Fhistorical ties to France.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
