OL,3,CJersey's Education Minister says he
OL,4,Ccannot support introducing bilingual
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FOn Jersey States Assembly social
OL,8,Fmedia, Deputy Bailhache says: "Studies
OL,9,Fhave also proved that the bilingual
OL,10,Fchild makes more rapid progress in
OL,11,Fother subjects too.
OL,13,F"Jersey is less than 15 miles from
OL,14,FFrance. It is our closest neighbour
OL,15,Fand French is one of our official
OL,16,Flanguages.
OL,18,F"If the States adopt my proposition
OL,19,Fthere would be in time enormous
OL,20,Fcultural and commercial benefits, both
OL,21,Ffor our children and for Jersey".
